STATE EX REL. BARNETTE
v.
SWEENEY 2019-0110 Supreme Court of Ohio. April 10, 2019 O'CONNOR, C.J., and KENNEDY, FRENCH, FISCHER, DEWINE, DONNELLY, and STEWART, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISION WITHOUT OPINION

On respondent's motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed. Relator's motion for leave denied as moot.
